WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:09.458 --> 00:00:14.216
Numbers is the most innovative and powerful
spreadsheet app ever designed for mobile device.

00:00:14.218 --> 00:00:19.958
It makes it easy to work with tables, charts,
formulas, photos and graphics on a flexible

00:00:19.960 --> 00:00:24.908
canvas that you control just by touching.

00:00:24.910 --> 00:00:28.266
Tap Numbers to get started.

00:00:28.268 --> 00:00:32.498
You'll find sixteen Apple design templates
that are perfect for whatever kind of project

00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:34.498
you're working on.

00:00:34.500 --> 00:00:38.138
You can also import any spreadsheet created
with Numbers on your Mac,

00:00:38.140 --> 00:00:41.648
or with Microsoft Excel on a Mac or PC.

00:00:41.650 --> 00:00:45.238
In Numbers you can have multiple sheets
with single spreadsheet

00:00:45.240 --> 00:00:47.978
and navigate them using tabs.

00:00:47.980 --> 00:00:51.998
Just touch any of the tabs
to switch between them.

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:52.826
To enter data,

00:00:52.828 --> 00:00:54.508
just double tap a cell,

00:00:54.510 --> 00:00:59.368
the intelligence on-screen keyboard is so smart
it knows just the type of data you'r entring

00:00:59.370 --> 00:01:01.978
and displays exactly the key layout you need,

00:01:01.980 --> 00:01:04.568
whether it's digits,

00:01:04.570 --> 00:01:06.138
duration,

00:01:06.140 --> 00:01:08.888
date and time,

00:01:08.890 --> 00:01:10.788
or texts.

00:01:10.790 --> 00:01:14.758
There's even a keyboard designed
just for entering formulas.

00:01:14.760 --> 00:01:17.156
Easily select to move columns with your finger,

00:01:17.158 --> 00:01:19.168
and drop them right where you want them.

00:01:19.170 --> 00:01:22.578
Your chart updates automatically
as you organize your data.

00:01:22.580 --> 00:01:28.258
You can add rows and columns to your table
to enter additional data or calculations.

00:01:28.260 --> 00:01:30.638
Numbers has a powerful calculation engine,

00:01:30.640 --> 00:01:35.398
with over two hundred fifty functions built-in,
including engineering,

00:01:35.400 --> 00:01:38.338
financial and statistical functions;

00:01:38.340 --> 00:01:40.468
all with clear concise help,

00:01:40.470 --> 00:01:44.188
so you can create advanced formulas quickly.

00:01:44.190 --> 00:01:46.998
Sum an entire column with just a touch,

00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:47.906
then tap "Fill"

00:01:47.908 --> 00:01:53.158
and drag to the right to quickly fill
that formulas for across the entire table.

00:01:53.160 --> 00:01:59.118
Numbers includes nine different types
of charts including bar, column and pie.

00:01:59.120 --> 00:02:02.988
Choose from a great-looking styles
that match your template.

00:02:02.990 --> 00:02:07.006
Use the chart options to adjust
the fonts, data labels

00:02:07.008 --> 00:02:09.596
and formats just how you want them.

00:02:09.598 --> 00:02:11.506
And emphasize part of your chart

00:02:11.508 --> 00:02:13.516
just drag a wedge to pull it out.

00:02:13.518 --> 00:02:14.358
With iPad

00:02:14.360 --> 00:02:17.831
it's simple to make your charts look great.

00:02:19.188 --> 00:02:23.076
iPad and Numbers are perfect
for entering data wherever you are.

00:02:23.078 --> 00:02:25.118
Set up the spreadsheet with the info you need

00:02:25.120 --> 00:02:29.256
and then use the built-in forms to added it.

00:02:29.258 --> 00:02:31.336
As you make the changes you want to the form

00:02:31.338 --> 00:02:33.198
your table updates automatically,

00:02:33.200 --> 00:02:35.396
because it's all link together.

00:02:35.398 --> 00:02:36.236
When you're ready,

00:02:36.238 --> 00:02:38.636
you can send your work via email,

00:02:38.638 --> 00:02:42.246
upload it to iWork.com so anyone
on a Mac or PC can view it,

00:02:42.248 --> 00:02:46.835
or easily export it as a Numbers or PDF file
so you can use it on your computer.

00:02:48.098 --> 00:02:50.706
You can buy Numbers from the App Store.

00:02:50.708 --> 00:02:52.148
With Numbers on iPad

00:02:52.150 --> 00:02:56.278
you've got the power to manage your data
and create stunning reports right in your hands.

